# Development Guide



## Option 2: Run Backend/Frontend Manually (Recommended for Development)

### 1. Start Infrastructure Only
```bash
docker compose up -d mongo mongo-express postgres keycloak
```

### 2. Run Backend Manually
```bash
cd backend
mvn clean package -DskipTests
mvn spring-boot:run
```
Backend runs on: http://localhost:8082

### 3. Run Frontend Manually
```bash
cd frontend
npm i --legacy-peer-deps
npm start
```
Frontend runs on: http://localhost:4200

## Access URLs
- Frontend: http://localhost:4200
- Backend API: http://localhost:8082/api
- Keycloak Admin: http://localhost:8080 (admin/admin)
- Mongo Express: http://localhost:8089 (admin/admin)

## Stop Services
```bash
# Stop all
docker compose down

# Stop and remove volumes
docker compose down -v
```


